data.description: Seller offering an additional $10,000 concession on a 2-1 buydown thru our preferred lender! Seller says SELL !  Huge $66K price reduction!   West Greeley opportunity in Homestead Heights!  Come inside this well maintained two-story home and enjoy the open floor plan. Large living room with gas fireplace and vaulted ceilings. The kitchen offers ample cabinet storage with plenty of counter space with breakfast bar, including all stainless steel appliances and separate dining area. Main level laundry and half bath. Upstairs you'll find the large primary bedroom with a full 5-piece updated bathroom including walk-in shower stall, soaker tub, and walk-in closet. Two additional large bedrooms as well as a bathroom upstairs. Fully finished basement with a large family room that is great for entertaining, and an extra bedroom. Fully fenced yard that backs to desired open space including front porch, storage shed and large patio. This home is in a great neighborhood within walking distance to Eagle Ridge pool, close to golf courses and shopping. Set up your showing and make it yours today!
